[
  {
    "startTime": 14.16,
    "endTime": 17.279,
    "text": "big boys don't cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.279,
    "endTime": 19.52,
    "text": "suck it up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.52,
    "endTime": 22.48,
    "text": "shut up and rub some dirt on it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.48,
    "endTime": 24.16,
    "text": "stop crying before i give you something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.16,
    "endTime": 26.16,
    "text": "to cry about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.16,
    "endTime": 28.16,
    "text": "these are just a few of the phrases that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.16,
    "endTime": 31.199,
    "text": "contribute to a disease in our society"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.199,
    "endTime": 34.48,
    "text": "and more specifically in our men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.48,
    "endTime": 36.32,
    "text": "it's a disease that has come to be known"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.32,
    "endTime": 37.2,
    "text": "as"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.2,
    "endTime": 39.92,
    "text": "toxic masculinity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.92,
    "endTime": 42.559,
    "text": "it's one i suffered a chronic case of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.559,
    "endTime": 45.76,
    "text": "so much so that i spent 24 years"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.76,
    "endTime": 47.36,
    "text": "of a life sentence in prison for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.36,
    "endTime": 52.16,
    "text": "kidnapping robbery and attempted murder"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.16,
    "endTime": 54.079,
    "text": "yet i'm here to tell you today that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.079,
    "endTime": 57.36,
    "text": "there's a solution for this epidemic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.36,
    "endTime": 59.28,
    "text": "i know for a fact the solution works"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.28,
    "endTime": 63.12,
    "text": "because i was a part of human trials"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.12,
    "endTime": 66.4,
    "text": "the solution is a mixture of elements"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.4,
    "endTime": 68.24,
    "text": "it begins with the willingness to look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.24,
    "endTime": 69.28,
    "text": "at your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.28,
    "endTime": 71.28,
    "text": "belief system and how out of alignment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.28,
    "endTime": 74.159,
    "text": "it is and how your actions negatively"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.159,
    "endTime": 76.24,
    "text": "impact not just yourself but the people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.24,
    "endTime": 78.24,
    "text": "around you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.24,
    "endTime": 80.479,
    "text": "the next ingredient is a willingness to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.479,
    "endTime": 83.439,
    "text": "be vulnerable with people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.439,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "who would not just support you but hold"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 88.72,
    "text": "you accountable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.72,
    "endTime": 90.56,
    "text": "but before i tell you about this i need"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.56,
    "endTime": 91.28,
    "text": "to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.28,
    "endTime": 94.72,
    "text": "let you know that in order to share this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.72,
    "endTime": 98.079,
    "text": "i have to bear my soul in full"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.079,
    "endTime": 101.119,
    "text": "and as i stand here with so many eyes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.119,
    "endTime": 103.119,
    "text": "fixed on me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.119,
    "endTime": 104.799,
    "text": "i feel raw"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.799,
    "endTime": 107.36,
    "text": "and naked"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.92,
    "endTime": 109.84,
    "text": "when this feeling is present i'm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.84,
    "endTime": 112.159,
    "text": "confident that the next phase of healing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.159,
    "endTime": 115.36,
    "text": "is on the horizon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.36,
    "endTime": 117.2,
    "text": "and that allows me to share my story in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 119.28,
    "text": "full"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.28,
    "endTime": 121.36,
    "text": "for all appearances sake i was born into"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.36,
    "endTime": 122.079,
    "text": "the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.079,
    "endTime": 124.719,
    "text": "ideal family dynamic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.719,
    "endTime": 127.68,
    "text": "mother father sister brother"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.68,
    "endTime": 128.72,
    "text": "bertha"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.72,
    "endTime": 130.16,
    "text": "eldridge jr"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.16,
    "endTime": 132.56,
    "text": "teddy ma and eldr iii"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.56,
    "endTime": 134.879,
    "text": "that's me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.879,
    "endTime": 136.8,
    "text": "my father was a vietnam veteran who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.8,
    "endTime": 138.64,
    "text": "earned a purple heart and made it home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.64,
    "endTime": 143.2,
    "text": "to find love mary and begin his own brew"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.2,
    "endTime": 145.04,
    "text": "so how did i wind up serving life in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.04,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "california prison system"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 150.4,
    "text": "keeping secrets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.4,
    "endTime": 152.48,
    "text": "believing the mantra that big boys don't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.48,
    "endTime": 154.56,
    "text": "cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.56,
    "endTime": 156.8,
    "text": "not knowing how to display any emotion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.8,
    "endTime": 160.4,
    "text": "confidently other than anger"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.12,
    "endTime": 163.12,
    "text": "participating in athletics and learning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.12,
    "endTime": 164.72,
    "text": "that the greater the performance on the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.72,
    "endTime": 166.239,
    "text": "field the less the need to worry about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.239,
    "endTime": 168.319,
    "text": "the rules off it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.319,
    "endTime": 170.8,
    "text": "it's hard to pin down any one specific"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.8,
    "endTime": 173.04,
    "text": "ingredient of the many symptoms that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.04,
    "endTime": 175.519,
    "text": "held me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.519,
    "endTime": 177.519,
    "text": "growing up as a young black male in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.519,
    "endTime": 179.84,
    "text": "sacramento california in the 1980s there"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.84,
    "endTime": 181.84,
    "text": "were two groups i identified as having"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.84,
    "endTime": 183.519,
    "text": "respect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.519,
    "endTime": 184.72,
    "text": "athletes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.72,
    "endTime": 187.36,
    "text": "and gangsters"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.36,
    "endTime": 190.08,
    "text": "i excelled in sports"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.08,
    "endTime": 191.92,
    "text": "that is until a friend and i chose to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.92,
    "endTime": 194.239,
    "text": "take his mom's car for a joyride and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.239,
    "endTime": 196.4,
    "text": "wreck it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.4,
    "endTime": 198.4,
    "text": "with my parents having to split the cost"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.4,
    "endTime": 200.48,
    "text": "of a total vehicle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.48,
    "endTime": 202.64,
    "text": "i was relegated to a summer of household"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.64,
    "endTime": 204.239,
    "text": "chores"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.239,
    "endTime": 206.8,
    "text": "and no sports"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.8,
    "endTime": 210.48,
    "text": "no sports meant no respect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.48,
    "endTime": 211.76,
    "text": "no respect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.76,
    "endTime": 214.08,
    "text": "equaled no power"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.08,
    "endTime": 218.0,
    "text": "power was vital to feed my illness"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 220.0,
    "text": "it was at that point the decision to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.0,
    "endTime": 222.799,
    "text": "transition from athlete"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.799,
    "endTime": 224.319,
    "text": "to gangster"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.319,
    "endTime": 228.08,
    "text": "was made and done so easily"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.08,
    "endTime": 230.64,
    "text": "early life experiences had set the stage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.64,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "for me to be well suited"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.0,
    "endTime": 237.36,
    "text": "to objectify others"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.519,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "act in a socially detached manner and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 241.439,
    "text": "above all else"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.439,
    "endTime": 243.28,
    "text": "seek to be viewed as in a position of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.28,
    "endTime": 245.599,
    "text": "power"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.599,
    "endTime": 248.64,
    "text": "a sense of power"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.2,
    "endTime": 253.68,
    "text": "equaled strength in my environment"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.68,
    "endTime": 255.36,
    "text": "but more importantly it did so in my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.36,
    "endTime": 256.88,
    "text": "mind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.88,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "my mind dictated my choices"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.0,
    "endTime": 262.32,
    "text": "my subsequent choices put me on the fast"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.32,
    "endTime": 265.12,
    "text": "track to prison life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.12,
    "endTime": 267.44,
    "text": "and even once in prison i continued my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.44,
    "endTime": 269.44,
    "text": "history of running over the rights of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.44,
    "endTime": 271.84,
    "text": "others"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.16,
    "endTime": 274.08,
    "text": "even knowing that that was the place"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.08,
    "endTime": 275.44,
    "text": "that i would die"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.44,
    "endTime": 278.08,
    "text": "once again i wound up in solitary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.08,
    "endTime": 279.6,
    "text": "confinement"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.6,
    "endTime": 281.68,
    "text": "for stabbing another prisoner nearly 30"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.68,
    "endTime": 283.84,
    "text": "times"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.24,
    "endTime": 285.84,
    "text": "i'd gotten to a place where i didn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.84,
    "endTime": 289.6,
    "text": "care how i lived or if i died"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.84,
    "endTime": 292.24,
    "text": "but then things changed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.24,
    "endTime": 293.68,
    "text": "one of the best things that happened in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.68,
    "endTime": 295.52,
    "text": "my life to that point was being sent to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.52,
    "endTime": 297.759,
    "text": "new folsom prison"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.759,
    "endTime": 300.479,
    "text": "once there i was approached to join a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.479,
    "endTime": 303.68,
    "text": "group called inside circle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.68,
    "endTime": 306.24,
    "text": "initially i was hesitant to join a group"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.24,
    "endTime": 308.479,
    "text": "referred to around the yard as hugga"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.479,
    "endTime": 311.479,
    "text": "thug"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.72,
    "endTime": 315.039,
    "text": "initially"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.039,
    "endTime": 317.52,
    "text": "that was yeah that was a little much but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.52,
    "endTime": 320.72,
    "text": "eventually i overcame my hesitancy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.72,
    "endTime": 322.4,
    "text": "as it turned out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.4,
    "endTime": 325.44,
    "text": "the circle was the vision of a man named"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.44,
    "endTime": 328.4,
    "text": "patrick nolan who was also serving life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.4,
    "endTime": 331.12,
    "text": "and who had grown sick and tired"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.12,
    "endTime": 333.52,
    "text": "of being sick and tired of watching us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.52,
    "endTime": 335.52,
    "text": "kill one another"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.52,
    "endTime": 336.84,
    "text": "over skin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.84,
    "endTime": 340.72,
    "text": "color rag color"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.8,
    "endTime": 342.639,
    "text": "being from northern or southern"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.639,
    "endTime": 344.8,
    "text": "california"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.8,
    "endTime": 346.56,
    "text": "or just plain breathing in the wrong"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.56,
    "endTime": 349.36,
    "text": "direction on a windy day"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.36,
    "endTime": 352.24,
    "text": "circle time is men sitting with men and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.24,
    "endTime": 355.28,
    "text": "cutting through the [ __ ]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.28,
    "endTime": 358.24,
    "text": "challenging structural ways of thinking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.24,
    "endTime": 360.72,
    "text": "i think the way that i think and i act"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.72,
    "endTime": 362.8,
    "text": "the way that i act"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.8,
    "endTime": 366.0,
    "text": "because i haven't questioned that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.0,
    "endTime": 367.6,
    "text": "like who said i should see a woman"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.6,
    "endTime": 370.479,
    "text": "walking down the street"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.479,
    "endTime": 373.36,
    "text": "turn around and check out her backside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.36,
    "endTime": 375.759,
    "text": "where did that come from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.759,
    "endTime": 377.84,
    "text": "if i don't question that i'll just go"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.84,
    "endTime": 381.479,
    "text": "along with the crowd"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.52,
    "endTime": 383.759,
    "text": "the locker room talk"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.759,
    "endTime": 385.919,
    "text": "in circle we sit and we question these"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 385.919,
    "endTime": 388.0,
    "text": "things why do i think the way that i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.0,
    "endTime": 390.96,
    "text": "think why do i act the way that i act"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.96,
    "endTime": 392.96,
    "text": "because when i get down to it i'm not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.96,
    "endTime": 396.0,
    "text": "thinking i'm not being an individual i'm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.0,
    "endTime": 398.479,
    "text": "not taking responsibility for who i am"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.479,
    "endTime": 402.08,
    "text": "and what it is i put into this world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.08,
    "endTime": 403.84,
    "text": "it was in a circle session that my life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.84,
    "endTime": 405.039,
    "text": "took a turn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.039,
    "endTime": 407.68,
    "text": "i remember being asked who i was and i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.68,
    "endTime": 409.84,
    "text": "didn't have an answer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.84,
    "endTime": 411.919,
    "text": "at least not one that felt honest in a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.919,
    "endTime": 414.72,
    "text": "room full of men who were seeking truth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.72,
    "endTime": 416.8,
    "text": "it would have been easy to say i'm a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.8,
    "endTime": 418.24,
    "text": "blood"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.24,
    "endTime": 419.12,
    "text": "or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.12,
    "endTime": 421.28,
    "text": "my name is vegas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.28,
    "endTime": 422.96,
    "text": "or any number of facades i had"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.96,
    "endTime": 425.52,
    "text": "manufactured to hide behind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.52,
    "endTime": 428.24,
    "text": "it was in that moment and in that venue"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.24,
    "endTime": 431.28,
    "text": "that the jig was up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.28,
    "endTime": 433.28,
    "text": "i realized that as sharp as i believed i"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.28,
    "endTime": 435.759,
    "text": "was i didn't even know who i was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.759,
    "endTime": 439.68,
    "text": "or why i acted the way that i acted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.88,
    "endTime": 443.12,
    "text": "i couldn't stand in a room full of men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.12,
    "endTime": 445.039,
    "text": "who were seeking to serve and support"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.039,
    "endTime": 448.88,
    "text": "and present an authentic me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.68,
    "endTime": 452.08,
    "text": "it was in that moment that i graduated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.08,
    "endTime": 453.68,
    "text": "to a place within that was ready for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.68,
    "endTime": 456.319,
    "text": "transformation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.319,
    "endTime": 457.919,
    "text": "for decades"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.919,
    "endTime": 460.08,
    "text": "i kept being the victim of molestation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.08,
    "endTime": 463.199,
    "text": "at the hands of a babysitter a secret"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.199,
    "endTime": 464.96,
    "text": "i submitted to this under the threat of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.96,
    "endTime": 467.28,
    "text": "my younger sister being harmed i was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.28,
    "endTime": 470.16,
    "text": "seven she was three"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.16,
    "endTime": 472.319,
    "text": "i believed it was my responsibility to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.319,
    "endTime": 475.12,
    "text": "keep her safe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.479,
    "endTime": 478.72,
    "text": "it was in that instant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.72,
    "endTime": 480.96,
    "text": "that the seeds were sown for a long"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.96,
    "endTime": 482.96,
    "text": "career of hurting others"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.96,
    "endTime": 487.52,
    "text": "be it physical mental or emotional"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.52,
    "endTime": 489.52,
    "text": "i developed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.52,
    "endTime": 491.599,
    "text": "in that instant"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.599,
    "endTime": 494.319,
    "text": "at seven years old the belief that going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.319,
    "endTime": 496.639,
    "text": "forward in life if a situation presented"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.639,
    "endTime": 498.639,
    "text": "itself where someone was going to get"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.639,
    "endTime": 499.68,
    "text": "hurt"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.68,
    "endTime": 502.4,
    "text": "i would be the one doing the hurting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.4,
    "endTime": 505.44,
    "text": "i also formulated the belief that loving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.44,
    "endTime": 507.759,
    "text": "put me in harm's way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.759,
    "endTime": 510.319,
    "text": "i also learned that caring about another"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.319,
    "endTime": 513.36,
    "text": "person made me weak"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 513.36,
    "endTime": 514.8,
    "text": "so not caring"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.8,
    "endTime": 517.919,
    "text": "that must equal strength"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.919,
    "endTime": 519.919,
    "text": "the greatest way to mask a shaky sense"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519.919,
    "endTime": 522.479,
    "text": "of self is to hide behind a false air of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.479,
    "endTime": 524.48,
    "text": "respect"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.48,
    "endTime": 526.48,
    "text": "sitting in circle resembles sitting in a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.48,
    "endTime": 527.519,
    "text": "fire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.519,
    "endTime": 532.399,
    "text": "it is a crucial that can and does break"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.48,
    "endTime": 535.6,
    "text": "it broke my old sense of self"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.6,
    "endTime": 536.959,
    "text": "diseased"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.959,
    "endTime": 538.72,
    "text": "value system"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.72,
    "endTime": 542.16,
    "text": "and way of looking at others"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.24,
    "endTime": 544.959,
    "text": "my old stale modes of thinking were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.959,
    "endTime": 546.88,
    "text": "invited into the open"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 546.88,
    "endTime": 548.64,
    "text": "to see if this is who i wanted to be in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.64,
    "endTime": 549.92,
    "text": "life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.92,
    "endTime": 551.68,
    "text": "i was accompanied by skilled"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.68,
    "endTime": 553.92,
    "text": "facilitators on a journey into the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.92,
    "endTime": 556.8,
    "text": "depths of myself to find those wounded"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.8,
    "endTime": 560.0,
    "text": "parts that not only festered"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.0,
    "endTime": 562.48,
    "text": "but seeped out to create unsafe space"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.48,
    "endTime": 565.12,
    "text": "for others"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 565.92,
    "endTime": 568.88,
    "text": "at times it resembled an exorcism"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.88,
    "endTime": 570.88,
    "text": "and in essence it was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.88,
    "endTime": 572.56,
    "text": "there was an extraction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.56,
    "endTime": 575.44,
    "text": "of old disease ways of thinking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.44,
    "endTime": 576.959,
    "text": "being"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.959,
    "endTime": 580.8,
    "text": "and reacting and an infusion of purpose"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.8,
    "endTime": 584.56,
    "text": "sitting in those circles saved my life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.64,
    "endTime": 587.2,
    "text": "i stand here today as a testament to the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.2,
    "endTime": 591.839,
    "text": "fact of the power of the work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.959,
    "endTime": 596.0,
    "text": "i was paroled in june 2014"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.0,
    "endTime": 598.08,
    "text": "following my third hearing before panel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.08,
    "endTime": 600.16,
    "text": "of former law enforcement officials who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.16,
    "endTime": 602.24,
    "text": "were tasked with determining my current"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.24,
    "endTime": 604.959,
    "text": "threat level to society"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.959,
    "endTime": 608.0,
    "text": "i stand here today for the first time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.0,
    "endTime": 610.959,
    "text": "since i was 14 years old not under any"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.959,
    "endTime": 613.04,
    "text": "form of state supervision"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.04,
    "endTime": 615.04,
    "text": "i'm married to a tremendous woman named"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.04,
    "endTime": 616.88,
    "text": "holly and together we're raising two"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.88,
    "endTime": 619.92,
    "text": "sons who i encourage"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.92,
    "endTime": 623.92,
    "text": "to experience emotions in a safe way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.92,
    "endTime": 626.72,
    "text": "i let them hold me when i cry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 626.72,
    "endTime": 628.88,
    "text": "they get to witness me not have all the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.88,
    "endTime": 630.079,
    "text": "answers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.079,
    "endTime": 632.56,
    "text": "my desire is for them to understand that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.56,
    "endTime": 635.12,
    "text": "being a man is not some machismo"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.12,
    "endTime": 636.88,
    "text": "caricature"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.88,
    "endTime": 639.68,
    "text": "and that characteristics usually defined"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 639.68,
    "endTime": 641.12,
    "text": "as weaknesses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.12,
    "endTime": 644.0,
    "text": "are parts of the whole healthy man"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.0,
    "endTime": 646.32,
    "text": "so today i continue the work not just on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.32,
    "endTime": 648.959,
    "text": "myself but in support of young males in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.959,
    "endTime": 651.12,
    "text": "my community"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.12,
    "endTime": 656.16,
    "text": "the challenge is to eradicate the cycle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.959,
    "endTime": 659.44,
    "text": "of emotional illiteracy and groupthink"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.44,
    "endTime": 661.279,
    "text": "that allows our males"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.279,
    "endTime": 663.68,
    "text": "to continue to victimize others as well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.68,
    "endTime": 665.36,
    "text": "as themselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.36,
    "endTime": 667.519,
    "text": "as a result of this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.519,
    "endTime": 669.44,
    "text": "they develop new ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.44,
    "endTime": 671.519,
    "text": "of how they want to show up in the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.519,
    "endTime": 673.12,
    "text": "and how they expect this world to show"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.12,
    "endTime": 675.2,
    "text": "up on their behalf"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.2,
    "endTime": 678.44,
    "text": "thank you"
  }
]